          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-1" n="1">Sir,<lb/><hi rend="display-initial">I</hi>N reading your Letter alone in my Hackney,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-2" n="2">Your Damnable Riddle my poor Brains did rack nigh,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-3" n="3">And when with much Labour the matter I crackt,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-4" n="4">I found you mistaken in Matter of Fact.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-5" n="5">A Woman's no <hi rend="italics">Sieve</hi> for with that you begin,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-6" n="6">Because she let's out, more than she takes in.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-7" n="7">And that a Woman's a <hi rend="italics">Riddle</hi> can never be right,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-8" n="8">For a <hi rend="italics">Riddle</hi> is dark, but a Woman is light.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-9" n="9">But hold──── you shall see, I can say something archer,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-10" n="10">Pray what is a Man? he's a fine Linnen Searcher.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-11" n="11">Now tell me a Thing that wants Interpretation,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-12" n="12">What Name for a Maid, was the first Man's Damnation.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-13" n="13">If your Worship will please t'explain me this <hi rend="italics">Rebus</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-14" n="14">I swear from hence forwards you shall be my <hi rend="italics">Phœbus</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-972-S899-line-15" n="15">om.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
